      <data key="d5">{"archivo": "projects/jpetstore/SequenceMapper.java"}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class sequence mapper located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper. Uses related classes sequence. Defines methods get sequence, update sequence."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The SequenceMapper class is responsible for managing sequences, providing operations to retrieve and update sequence values. It appears to interact with a Sequence entity, offering methods to get and update sequence values."</data>
