      <data key="d6">"Java class sequence located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Defines methods get name, get next id, sequence, set name, set next id."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The Sequence class is responsible for managing a sequence of IDs, providing methods to retrieve the next ID and to set the name and next ID of the sequence. It encapsulates the logic for generating and managing sequence IDs."</data>
