      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{"archivo": "projects/jpetstore/CartActionBean.java"}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class cart action bean located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions. Inherits from abstract action bean. Uses related classes cart, cart item, catalog service, item. Defines methods add item to cart, check out, clear, get cart, remove item from cart, set cart, set working item id, update cart quantities, view cart."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The CartActionBean class is responsible for managing a shopping cart, providing operations to add, remove, and update items, as well as checkout and clear the cart. It interacts with the Cart and related classes to perform these actions."</data>
