    <node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions.AbstractActionBean">
      <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions.AbstractActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d1">"AbstractActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
      <data key="d3">""</data>
      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class abstract action bean located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions. Defines methods get context, set context, set message."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The AbstractActionBean class is responsible for managing a context, providing methods to get and set the context, and to display a message. It appears to be a base class for handling actions in a web application."</data>
