    <node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain.Category">
      <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain.Category"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Category"</data>
      <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
      <data key="d3">""</data>
      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class category located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.domain. Defines methods get category id, get description, get name, set category id, set description, set name, to string."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The Category class is responsible for managing category data, providing operations to retrieve and update its name and description, as well as its unique identifier. It also provides a string representation of the category."</data>
