    <node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper.LineItemMapper">
      <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper.LineItemMapper"</data>
      <data key="d1">"LineItemMapper"</data>
      <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
      <data key="d3">"Clase LineItemMapper"</data>
      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{"archivo": "projects/jpetstore/LineItemMapper.java"}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class line item mapper located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper. Uses related classes line item. Defines methods get line items by order id, insert line item."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The LineItemMapper class is responsible for managing LineItem objects, providing operations to retrieve and insert them. It offers methods to get LineItems by order ID and insert new LineItems."</data>
