      <data key="d6">"Java class product mapper located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper. Uses related classes product. Defines methods get product, get product list by category, search product list."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The ProductMapper class is responsible for managing Product data, providing operations to retrieve and search products. It offers methods to get a single product, a list of products by category, and a list of products based on a search query."</data>
