    <node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions.OrderActionBean">
      <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions.OrderActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d1">"OrderActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
      <data key="d3">"Clase OrderActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{"archivo": "projects/jpetstore/OrderActionBean.java"}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class order action bean located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions. Inherits from abstract action bean. Uses related classes account action bean, cart action bean, order, order service. Defines methods clear, get credit card types, get order, get order id, get order list, is confirmed, is shipping address required, list orders, new order, new order form, set confirmed, set order, set order id, set shipping address required, view order."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The OrderActionBean class is responsible for managing orders, providing operations to create, view, and update orders, as well as retrieve order information. It appears to be a controller or action handler for order-related functionality in a web application."</data>
