    <node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions.CatalogActionBean">
      <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions.CatalogActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d1">"CatalogActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
      <data key="d3">"Clase CatalogActionBean"</data>
      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{"archivo": "projects/jpetstore/CatalogActionBean.java"}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class catalog action bean located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.web.actions. Inherits from abstract action bean. Uses related classes catalog service, category, item, product. Defines methods clear, get category, get category id, get category list, get item, get item id, get item list, get keyword, get product, get product id, get product list, search products, set category, set category id, set category list, set item, set item id, set item list, set keyword, set product, set product id, set product list, view category, view item, view main, view product."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The CatalogActionBean class is responsible for managing a catalog of products, categories, and items, providing operations to retrieve, update, and search catalog data. It interacts with related classes such as CatalogService, Category, Item, and Product to perform these operations."</data>
