    <node id="class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper.ItemMapper">
      <data key="d0">"class:org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper.ItemMapper"</data>
      <data key="d1">"ItemMapper"</data>
      <data key="d2">"clase"</data>
      <data key="d3">""</data>
      <data key="d4">{"fan_in": 0, "fan_out": 0}</data>
      <data key="d5">{}</data>
      <data key="d6">"Java class item mapper located in package org.mybatis.jpetstore.mapper. Uses related classes item. Defines methods get inventory quantity, get item, get item list by product, update inventory quantity."</data>
      <data key="d7">"The ItemMapper class is responsible for managing Item data, providing operations to retrieve and update inventory quantities and item information. It offers methods to get item details, list items by product, and update inventory quantities."</data>
